.It Sy initialize
All initializations to cease
.It Sy replace
All device replacements to cease
.It Sy remove
Device removal to cease
.It Sy resilver
Resilver to cease
.It Sy scrub
Scrub to cease
.It Sy trim
Manual trim to cease
.El
.Pp
